  "extras": {
    "summary": "AN ACT TO ENACT THE \"RETAILER TAX FAIRNESS ACT\"; TO DEFINE CERTAIN TERMS RELATING TO ELECTRONIC PAYMENT TRANSACTIONS; TO PROVIDE THAT A MERCHANT OR SELLER COLLECTING STATE TAXES OR LOCAL TAXES FROM A PURCHASER IN ANY ELECTRONIC PAYMENT TRANSACTION FOR WHICH THE MERCHANT OR SELLER PAYS OR IS CHARGED AN INTERCHANGE FEE WILL BE ENTITLED TO A CREDIT AGAINST SUCH TAXES; TO PROVIDE FOR THE AMOUNT OF THE TAX CREDIT; AND FOR RELATED PURPOSES."
  },
